s e Componentes**\n- **Pâ”œأ­ginas:** `/leaderboard`\n- **Componentes/Arquivos:** `LeaderboardPage`, `Top3Cards`, `LeaderboardTable`.\n\n**Padrâ”œأ؛o de Layout e Cores**\n- Famâ”œآ،lia C (bento grid).\n\n**Validaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes**\n- Private mode: ocultar/anonimizar user.\n\n**API**\n- `GET /api/v1/leaderboard?range=7d|all&q=...`\n\n**Detalhes Tâ”œآ®cnicos (Lint AI)**\n- **Path:** `src/app/features/leaderboard/`\n- **Privacy:** Se `user.privacy_mode === true`, exibir como \"Anonymous User\" e ocultar avatar.\n- **Visual:** Top 3 em cards destacados no topo (Bento Grid).\n\n**Critâ”œآ®rios de Aceite**\n- Busca, filtro e paginaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o funcionam; private mode aplicado.\n\n**Checklist**\n- [ ] Top3 renderiza\n- [ ] Tabela paginada\n- [ ] Private mode\n\n**Git (Branch e PR)**\n- **Branch:** `feature/FE-16-leaderboard`\n- **Commits:** `feat(frontend): ...`\n- **PR:** `develop`\n- **Revisor:** 1+\n\n**Dependâ”œآ¬ncias**\n- **Pode fazer em paralelo?** Sim\n- **Depende de:** BE leaderboard endpoint","createdAt":"2026-04-18T16:22:52Z","labels":[{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w1tA","name":"area:frontend","description":"Frontend tasks","color":"1f6feb"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w3SQ","name":"phase:ux","description":"UX improvements","color":"d73a4a"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w4yg","name":"type:feature","description":"Feature work","color":"0e8a16"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w6Kg","name":"parallel:yes","description":"Can run in parallel","color":"7057ff"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w7jQ","name":"priority:medium","description":"Medium priority","color":"fbca04"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w82Q","name":"sprint:3","description":"Sprint 3","color":"d4c5f9"}],"number":18,"state":"OPEN","title":"FE-16 - Leaderboard (Top3 + tabela + filtros + private mode)"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"**Contexto**\n- Operaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o do protocolo (TTL + distribuiâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o) exige UI administrativa segura.\n\n**Objetivo**\n- Criar painel admin com aâ”œآ؛â”œأپes de keeper e distribuiâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de impacto.\n\n**Racional (por que isso existe)**\n- **Operaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o Soroban:** TTL/state rent exige manutenâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o real.\n- **Fechamento do ciclo:** distribuiâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o de impacto precisa ocorrer e ser auditâ”œأ­vel.\n- **Seguranâ”œآ؛a:** UI separada por role reduz risco operacional.\n\n**Escopo**\n- UI/admin flows; sem alterar lâ”œâ”‚gica do contrato.\n\n**Objetivo detalhado**\n- Listar markets elegâ”œآ،veis.\n- Selecionar markets e chamar batch bump TTL.\n- Executar distribute impact por market com confirmaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o.\n\n**Pâ”œأ­ginas e Componentes**\n- **Pâ”œأ­ginas:** `/admin/keeper`, `/admin/markets`\n- **Componentes/Arquivos:** `AdminGuard`, `KeeperTTLTable`, `DistributeImpactButton`.\n\n**Padrâ”œأ؛o de Layout e Cores**\n- Famâ”œآ،lia C; aâ”œآ؛â”œأپes perigosas devem ter confirmaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o e destaque (warning).\n\n**Validaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes**\n- Somente `role=admin`.\n- Confirmaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o antes de executar aâ”œآ؛â”œأپes.\n\n**API**\n- `POST /api/v1/admin/keeper/batch-bump-ttl`\n- `POST /api/v1/admin/markets/{id}/distribute-impact`\n\n**Critâ”œآ®rios de Aceite**\n- Admin consegue executar aâ”œآ؛â”œأپes e ver status por market.\n\n**Checklist**\n- [ ] Role guard\n- [ ] Status por item\n- [ ] Confirmaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o em aâ”œآ؛â”œأپes crâ”œآ،ticas\n\n**Git (Branch e PR)**\n- **Branch:** `feature/FE-15-admin-panel`\n- **Commits:** `feat(frontend): ...`\n- **PR:** `develop`\n- **Revisor:** 1+\n\n**Dependâ”œآ¬ncias**\n- **Pode fazer em paralelo?** Nâ”œأ؛o\n- **Depende de:** BE admin/keeper endpoints + SC batch_bump_ttl/distribute","createdAt":"2026-04-18T16:22:52Z","labels":[{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w1tA","name":"area:frontend","description":"Frontend tasks","color":"1f6feb"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w2Ow","name":"phase:setup","description":"Setup/infra","color":"0e8a16"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w4yg","name":"type:feature","description":"Feature work","color":"0e8a16"},{"id":"