ncy)"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"**Contexto**\n- Ledger pâ”œâ•‘blico de impacto â”œآ® uma das peâ”œآ؛as centrais de transparâ”œآ¬ncia do produto.\n\n**Objetivo**\n- Implementar tela de ledger com filtros e export.\n\n**Racional (por que isso existe)**\n- **Transparâ”œآ¬ncia:** prova pâ”œâ•‘blica de distribuiâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o e resultados.\n- **Auditoria:** export facilita compliance e investigaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o.\n\n**Escopo**\n- UI + integraâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o com export job; sem alterar lâ”œâ”‚gica do backend.\n\n**Objetivo detalhado**\n- Filtros combinâ”œأ­veis e paginaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o.\n- Modal de export e acompanhamento do status do job.\n\n**Pâ”œأ­ginas e Componentes**\n- **Pâ”œأ­ginas:** `/impact/ledger`\n- **Componentes/Arquivos:** `ImpactLedgerPage`, `FilterBar`, `ExportModal`, `LedgerTable`.\n\n**Padrâ”œأ؛o de Layout e Cores**\n- Famâ”œآ،lia C (Dashboard) com أ”أ‡آ£glass-cardأ”أ‡أک; botâ”œأپes neutros para export.\n\n**Validaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes**\n- Validar filtros (range/time/size) e impedir combinaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes invâ”œأ­lidas (se existir).\n\n**API**\n- `GET /api/v1/impact/ledger`\n- `POST /api/v1/impact/ledger/export`\n- `GET /api/v1/impact/ledger/export/{id}`\n\n**Detalhes Tâ”œآ®cnicos (Lint AI)**\n- **Path:** `src/app/features/impact/ledger/`\n- **Export Flow:** \n  1. `POST /api/v1/impact/ledger/export` -> returns `job_id`.\n  2. Polling `GET /api/v1/impact/ledger/export/{id}` until `status === 'done'`.\n  3. `window.open(file_url)`.\n\n**Critâ”œآ®rios de Aceite**\n- Filtros aplicam e resetam paginaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o.\n- Export gera arquivo e permite download.\n\n**Checklist**\n- [ ] Filtros\n- [ ] Export modal\n- [ ] Download final\n\n**Git (Branch e PR)**\n- **Branch:** `feature/FE-11-impact-ledger`\n- **Commits:** `feat(frontend): ...`, `test(frontend): ...`\n- **PR:** `develop`\n- **Revisor:** 1+\n\n**Dependâ”œآ¬ncias**\n- **Pode fazer em paralelo?** Sim\n- **Depende de:** BE impact ledger + export jobs","createdAt":"2026-04-18T16:22:49Z","labels":[{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w1tA","name":"area:frontend","description":"Frontend tasks","color":"1f6feb"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w2-g","name":"phase:core","description":"Core features","color":"5319e7"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w4yg","name":"type:feature","description":"Feature work","color":"0e8a16"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w6Kg","name":"parallel:yes","description":"Can run in parallel","color":"7057ff"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w61Q","name":"priority:high","description":"High priority","color":"d73a4a"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w82Q","name":"sprint:3","description":"Sprint 3","color":"d4c5f9"}],"number":13,"state":"OPEN","title":"FE-11 - Global Impact Feed + Export"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"**Contexto**\n- Governanâ”œآ؛a de impacto: crâ”œآ®ditos = floor(sqrt(stake_stroops)); custo = votosâ”¬â–“.\n\n**Objetivo**\n- Implementar tela de voting com validaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes e fluxo de assinatura.\n\n**Racional (por que isso existe)**\n- **Mecanismo de justiâ”œآ؛a:** voto quadrâ”œأ­tico reduz dominâ”œأ³ncia de baleias.\n- **Fechamento do ciclo:** winners direcionam impacto social de forma transparente.\n\n**Escopo**\n- UI de sliders + câ”œأ­lculo + build-vote + assinatura.\n\n**Objetivo detalhado**\n- Renderizar lista de ONGs.\n- Ajustar sliders e custo.\n- Impedir exceder crâ”œآ®ditos.\n- Confirmar submissâ”œأ؛o أ”أ‡آ£finalأ”أ‡أک.\n\n**Pâ”œأ­ginas e Componentes**\n- **Pâ”œأ­ginas:** `/voting` (ou equivalente)\n- **Componentes/Arquivos:** `VotingPage`, `NgoVoteCard`, `VoteSummaryBar`, `VoteService`.\n\n**Padrâ”œأ؛o de Layout e Cores**\n- Slider fill em verde primâ”œأ­rio; cards disabled em grayscale/opacity.\n\n**Validaâ”œآ؛â”œأپes**\n- `allocated_votes^2` nâ”œأ؛o excede credits.\n- Bloquear se jâ”œأ­ votou.\n\n**API**\n- `GET /api/v1/governance/organizations` (ou `/ngos` conforme backend)\n- `POST /api/v1/transactions/build-vote`\n- WS tx status\n\n**Detalhes Tâ”œآ®cnicos (Lint AI)**\n- **Path:** `src/app/features/voting/`\n- **Logic:** \n  - `credits = profile.voice_credits` (ou calculado localmente como `floor(sqrt(stake))`).\n  - `current_cost = sum(votes^2)`.\n  - Block submit if `current_cost > credits`.\n- **States:** `has_voted` (Boolean) -> desabilita sliders.\n- **Testes:** `voting.component.spec.ts` quadratic cost calculation.\n\n**Critâ”œآ®rios de Aceite**\n- Voto submetido e UI travada apâ”œâ”‚s confirmaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o.\n\n**Checklist**\n- [ ] Total credits correto\n- [ ] Travamento por excesso\n- [ ] Modal confirmaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o\n\n**Git (Branch e PR)**\n- **Branch:** `feature/FE-10-voting-quadratic`\n- **Commits:** `feat(frontend): ...`, `test(frontend): ...`\n- **PR:** `develop`\n- **Revisor:** 1+\n\n**Dependâ”œآ¬ncias**\n- **Pode fazer em paralelo?** Nâ”œأ؛o\n- **Depende de:** BE build-vote + ONGs + worker","createdAt":"2026-04-18T16:22:48Z","labels":[{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w1tA","name":"area:frontend","description":"Frontend tasks","color":"1f6feb"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w2-g","name":"phase:core","description":"Core features","color":"5319e7"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w4yg","name":"type:feature","description":"Feature work","color":"0e8a16"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w6dw","name":"parallel:no","description":"Should run sequentially","color":"8e7cc3"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w61Q","name":"priority:high","description":"High priority","color":"d73a4a"},{"id":"LA_kwDOR9LNQM8AAAACf2w8xw","name":"sprint:2","description":"Sprint 2","color":"bfdadc"}],"number":12,"state":"OPEN","title":"FE-10 - Voting Quadrâ”œأ­tico (voice credits sqrt + votos finais)"},{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMDM0Nzcw","is_bot":false,"login":"heliocarrara","name":"Helio Carrara"},"body":"**Contexto**\n- Pull over push: usuâ”œأ­rio deve acionar claim para receber payout.\n\n**Objetivo**\n- Tela de claims e fluxo de claim (build-claim أ”أ¥أ† wallet أ”أ¥أ† confirmaâ”œآ؛â”œأ؛o).\n\n**Racional (por que